        "title": "8. `agent.py`",
        "content": "\n**Gaps:** `cmd_db_new`'s posted-days filtering/first-seen-group truncation (the trickiest logic in the file — explicitly the subject of an in-code comment about not splitting groups), `cmd_db_mark` validation, `_normalize_ats`'s tag/text-node split (must not touch `<style>`/`<script>`/attribute text), `_chrome_bin` discovery order, `main()`'s subcommand/flag-splitting dispatch.\n\n```python\n",
